WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.533 --> 00:00:02.566
I am very satisfied with your performance. You can go out first.

2
00:00:02.566 --> 00:00:04.066
Mom and I have something to talk about

3
00:00:07.133 --> 00:00:10.866
Du Chen, you heard what we just said

4
00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:14.566
I heard what I should have heard and what I shouldn't have heard anyway

5
00:00:14.566 --> 00:00:16.800
Du Chen, don't misunderstand

6
00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:19.266
We were just talking.

7
00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:22.100
What a 2 billion

8
00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:23.433
You can ask me to borrow it.

9
00:00:23.500 --> 00:00:25.166
I can call your account tomorrow.

10
00:00:25.166 --> 00:00:26.700
You want to lend me 2 billion

11
00:00:26.766 --> 00:00:29.300
I can give you 2 billion

12
00:00:30.100 --> 00:00:31.900
I can also give you hundreds of millions every day.

13
00:00:32.133 --> 00:00:34.200
It depends on how you choose, little mother.

14
00:00:34.600 --> 00:00:36.566
Du Chen, don't do this

15
00:00:36.566 --> 00:00:38.100
I'm your little mother

16
00:00:38.466 --> 00:00:40.266
My dad has been dead for so many years

17
00:00:40.266 --> 00:00:42.266
Are you really going to be a widow?

18
00:00:42.266 --> 00:00:46.000
Or are you having an affair with my brother too?

19
00:00:47.066 --> 00:00:50.333
Du Chen, I warn you not to talk nonsense

20
00:00:50.333 --> 00:00:52.233
I have nothing to do with your brother

21
00:00:52.566 --> 00:00:54.233
Then why are you helping him?

22
00:00:54.800 --> 00:00:57.700
It was the decision of the entire consortium to make him the head of the family

23
00:00:57.700 --> 00:00:59.333
And of course I helped him.

24
00:00:59.333 --> 00:01:01.200
Hum of course

25
00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:02.400
Are you kidding me?

26
00:01:02.400 --> 00:01:04.933
My father's will clearly states that I am the heir

27
00:01:04.933 --> 00:01:06.666
You have to support this Du Feiyu

28
00:01:06.766 --> 00:01:08.600
What do you take for granted

29
00:01:08.600 --> 00:01:10.933
Or you and my brother

30
00:01:10.933 --> 00:01:12.966
There is a secret between you

